question: What restaurant is available as I head towards Lawrence Recreation Center;Rutland Historical Society Museum, VT within 170 kilometers from Sparrow Art Supply, Middlebury, VT?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.168916 44.013286)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-72.974829 43.606735)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.168916 44.013286)',4326)::geography, 170000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.168916 44.013286)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
